  "text": "GADD45B belongs to GADD45 genes family and proteins encoded by this family and recognized as stress sensors in signaling responses to various physiological or environmental stresses. GADD45 genes family mediates their activity via interactions with other cellular proteins [CITATION_1] and can inhibit cell proliferation at different stages and induce cell apoptosis [CITATION_2] .",
